@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="container mt-4">

    <div class="mb-4">
        <h1 class="mb-2">Test Management System</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">
            Your free lightweight test platform for education and corporate training.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">

        <!-- Teachers -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">For teachers</h5>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">
                        <b>Create tests, manage questions, assign students and review results.</b>
                        <br />
                        Suitable for educational courses and internal company assessments.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Students -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">For students</h5>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">
                        <b>Take assigned tests, track your progress and review completed results.</b>
                        <br />
                        Designed to keep the test process simple, fast and transparent.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Admin -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Administration</h5>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">
                        <b>Manage users, assign teacher and student roles, and control access to tests and training flows.</b>
                        <br />
                        Designed for school administrators and corporate HR teams.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <hr class="my-4" />

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p class="text-muted">
                <i>This free application is built as a practical PET project to demonstrate real-world architecture using ASP.NET Core, Blazor and EF Core. It focuses on clear separation of concerns, role-based access and easily maintainable business logic.</i>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
